20#ifndef GCC_TREE_SSA_THREADEDGE_H
21#define GCC_TREE_SSA_THREADEDGE_H
22
23extern vec<tree> ssa_name_values;
24#define SSA_NAME_VALUE(x) \
25 (SSA_NAME_VERSION (x) < ssa_name_values.length () \
26 ? ssa_name_values[SSA_NAME_VERSION (x)] \
27 : NULL_TREE)
28extern void set_ssa_name_value (tree, tree);
29extern void threadedge_initialize_values (void);
30extern void threadedge_finalize_values (void);
31extern bool potentially_threadable_block (basic_block);
32extern void propagate_threaded_block_debug_into (basic_block, basic_block);
33extern void thread_outgoing_edges (basic_block, gcond *,
34 const_and_copies *,
35 avail_exprs_stack *,
36 tree (*) (gimple *, gimple *,
37 avail_exprs_stack *, basic_block));
38
39#endif /* GCC_TREE_SSA_THREADEDGE_H */
